thread.title: Daniel Najvar
thread.title_full: Disc Makers reviewed by Daniel Najvar

author: Daniel Najvar
title: Daniel Najvar
text: The process of having my song mastered at The Soundlab was so easy. It was even returned to me in less time than was predicted (3 days). The end result was something that I wasn't expecting either. The process made my song sound great across every platform I could play it on.
